  "text": "The ESTCube-1 employs a CMOS MT9V011 along with a microcontroller STM32F217ZG of ARM Cortex M3 architecture that implements a dedicated interface for image sensors and additionally has a flexible static memory controller (FSMC) which allows easy connection to an external static random access memory (SRAM) [CITATION_1] . On the other hand, the University of Tartu does not provide information about the control software.",
